                "text": "<p>Since every batch of Milton’s Popcorn is made fresh and ready to enjoy, we do not offer refunds or exchanges once your order is placed. </p><p>If your order arrives damaged, incorrect, or defective, please contact us immediately at [Insert support email] with your order number and photos of the issue.</p><p>We’ll make it right with a replacement, discount, or store credit—because every kernel counts at Milton’s.</p><p>Please note that we cannot accept returns of opened or partially consumed produts.</p>",
