              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We ship Monday through Friday, and most orders are processed within 3 business days.</p><p>You can select your preferred carrier (UPS or FedEx) at checkout. Once your order is shipped, shipping charges are non-refundable.</p><p>Warm Weather Advisory: Some products (like caramel or chocolate-covered popcorn) may melt in high temperatures.We recommend selecting 2-Day or Overnight Shipping, which includes complimentary cold packs during warm seasons.</p><p>If your shipping address is entered incorrectly or requires an update after shipment, a $20 address correction fee may apply.</p>",
